about.summary: Convert a logical vector or a vector of p-values or a correlation, difference, or distance matrix into a display identifying the pairs for which the differences were not significantly different.  Designed for use in conjunction with the output of functions like TukeyHSD, dist{stats}, simint, simtest, csimint, csimtest{multcomp}, friedmanmc, kruskalmc{pgirmess}.

Convert a logical vector or a vector of p-values or a correlation, difference, or distance matrix into a display identifying the pairs for which the differences were not significantly different.  Designed for use in conjunction with the output of functions like TukeyHSD, dist{stats}, simint, simtest, csimint, csimtest{multcomp}, friedmanmc, kruskalmc{pgirmess}.

name: r-multcompview
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.1-10" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-multcompview
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  fn: multcompView_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/multcompView_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/multcompView/multcompView_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 38f249b22758c9f727b1656d1a08c6022a06a1ea319364ff680147d64598ad8a

build:
  noarch: generic
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('multcompView')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('multcompView')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=multcompView
  license: GPL-2.0 and GPL-3.0
  summary: Convert a logical vector or a vector of p-values or a correlation, difference, or distance matrix into a display identifying the pairs for which the differences were not significantly different.  Designed for use in conjunction with the output of functions like TukeyHSD, dist{stats}, simint, simtest, csimint,
    csimtest{multcomp}, friedmanmc, kruskalmc{pgirmess}.
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
